data.description: This 4 bedroom 3 full bath home with an over sized loft is ready for a new family to call home. ADDED BONUS  one bedroom and full bath is located downstairs. Great for multi generational use.  Brand new HVAC installed. Lets chat location~ minutes from Luke Air Force Base.  For all you football fans, Cardinals stadium is less than 10 min drive.  Westgate Entertainment District  is the place to be.  Dining options are endless, Shopping galore. Ready to hit a slot machine? Desert Diamond Casino is at your finger tips. Check out Tiger woods new concept Pop Stroke. This location is unbeatable. Welcome to Glendale, AZ.
